A BILL
for
1 AN ACT relating to the Wyoming Legal Tender Act; requiring
2 the state treasurer to hold and invest specie and specie
3 legal tender; authorizing the state treasurer to hire
4 consultants; providing rulemaking authority; requiring a
5 study and report; and providing for effective dates.
6
7 Be It Enacted by the Legislature of the State of Wyoming:
8
9 Section 1. W.S. 9-4-1306 is created to read:
10
11 9-4-1306. State treasurer duties; consultants;
12 rulemaking authority.
13
14 (a) The state treasurer shall implement this article
15 by:
